quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  57,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuji e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo, √Ďee√Īo on."
  57,2,"Ko KaŇčko heeranii laamu kammuuji …óiin e lesdi ndin. Himo wuurna Himo wara, KanŇčko O kattan…óo kala hu'unde."
  57,3,"Ko KaŇčko woni arano e cakkitii…óo, pee√Īu…óo e birnii…óo, KaŇčko ko O ganndu…óo kala hu'unde."
  57,4,"Ko KaŇčko tagi kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndiin ndeer bal…óe jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka dow ""Arsi""; Himo anndi ko mutata kon ka leydi, e ko ∆īawata e mayri, e ko jipporta ka kammu e ko ∆īawata e maggu. Homo wonndi e mon kala ka ngon…óon. Allah no reeni ko ngolloton kon."
  57,5,"Ko KaŇčko heeranii laamu kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin. Ko ka Allah fiyakuuji …óin nduttirtee."
  57,6,"Himo naadia jemma on e ndeer √Īalawma on, o naadira √Īalama on kadi e ndeer jemma on. KaŇčko ko O ganndu…óo ko woni e ndeer …ďer…óe."
  57,7,"GooŇč…óinee Allah e nulaa…óo makko on, nafqon kon ko o wa…óiri on lomtinaa…ďe e mum. GooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen e mon, …ďe nafqi [jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen], hino woodani …ďeen njo…ďdi mawnundi."
  57,8,"E ko he…ďi on, on ngooŇč…óintaa Allah? E hino Nulaa…óo on hino nodda on e gooŇč…óingol Joomi mon. Goo…óii [Allah] ∆īettii e mon ahadi, si on laatike gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  57,9,"Ko KaŇčko jippinta e jeyaa…óo makko on aayeeje …ďanngu…óe, fii no o njaltinira on e ni…ďe fa'ade e ndaygu. Pellet, Allah ko jurmotoo…óo on, jaafotoo…óo."
  57,10,"E ko he…ďi on, on cakkotaako fii laawol Allah ngol, e hino le ko Allah woodani ronugol kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin? Fotataa e mon, …ďen sakkinoo…ďe ado uddital ngal …ďe ha…ďidaa; ko …ďeen …ďuri mawnude darja e dii …ďeen sakkii…ďe …ďaawo …óum …ďe ha…ďidaa. ∆Āe fof ma…ď…ďe noon, Allah fodii …ďe mo∆ī∆īere. Allah no humpitii ko ngolloton kon."
  57,11,"Ko hommbo √Īamlirta Allah √Īamaande labaande, o sowana mo nde, hara no woodani mo njo…ďdi teddundi?"
  57,12,"√Ďande nji'oytaa gooŇč…óin…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen e gooŇč…óin…ďe rew…ďe …ďeen, hara annoora ma…ď…ďe yaara ye'eso ma…ď…ďe e √Īaamo ma…ď…ďe (…ďe mbi'anee): ""Weltaare mon hannde ko Aljannaaji, …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley mum, ko on duumotoo…ďe ndeer ton"". Ko …óum woni malal mawngal ngal."
  57,13,"√Ďalnde naafiqii…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen e naafiqii…ďe rew…ďe …ďen mbi'anoyta gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen: ""kabbee min, min njalbinora annoora mon on"". ∆Āe mbi'anee : ""Yiltoree …ďaawo mon, …óa…ď…ďoyon annoora"". Heedo wa…óee hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ngo damal ngal yurmeende woni e nder mum, …ďaawo maggal noon, ko lepte woni e bannge mum."
  57,14,"Hi…ďe nodda …ďe : ""E min ngondaano e mon?"" ∆Āe mbi'a : ""Ko non nhoniri. Ko woni tun, on fitinno ko'e mon, habbitani…óon [gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen bone], cikkiti…óon, yelaaji hodi on haa yamiroore Allah nden ari. Hodoowo on hodi on e mo∆ī∆īere Allah ndeen."
  57,15,"Hannde noon, on nja…ďantaake coktor…óum wonaa e …ďeen yeddu…ďe. Depporde mon nden ko ka Yiite : ko ngen woni ko hanndu…óon. Nge bonii ruttorde."
  57,16,"E yontaani gooŇč…óii…ďe …ďen nde …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen dee∆īirta jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippii immorde e goonga? Hara …ďe wa'aani wa …ďeen okkanoo…ďe defte …ďen ko adii, dumunna on juutani …ďeen, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen njo'ori, ko …óuu…óunoo e ma…ď…ďe ko ko faasiqii…ďe."
  57,17,"Nganndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay lesdi ndiin …ďaawo ndi yo'orii. GooŇč…óii Min …ďannginiranii on aayeeje …óeen, fii no haqqiliron."
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotoo…ďe (jaw…óe mum …ďeen) ka wor…ďe e ka rew…ďe …ďe √Īami Allah √Īamaande labaande, …ďe sowanoyte (mbarjaari) hara no woodani …ďe njo…ďdi mawndi."
  57,19,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óin…ďe Allah e Nulaa…óo makko on, ko …ďen woni goongiyaŇčke en. Sahodin…ďe …ďen ka Joomi mun, hino woodani …ďen njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe e annoora ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āeen noon yeddu…ďe …ďe njeddi aayeeje Amen …óeen, ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe Jahiimi ngen."
  57,20,"Ngnndee won'de nguurndam aduna …óam ko fijindaaru, e mbelee…óe, e cu…óaari, e …ďurondiro hakkunde mon e jaw…óe e …ďi…ď…ďe. Wano to…ďo haawnungo remoo…ďe …ďen pu…ói mum, refti ngo yo'ora, yi'aa hingo soy…ói; refti ngo wonta muncii…óum. Hino ka laakara, lette ca…ótu…óe, e yaafuyee immorde e Allah e yarluyee. Nguurndam aduna …óam wonaani, si wonaa dakammehoy hodo."
  57,21,"Ngadondiree e (golle) yaafaawuya ka Joomi mon, e Aljanna mo yaajeendi mun wa'i yaajeendi kammu ngun e leydi ndin, on maranaama …ďren gooŇč…óin…ďe Allah e Nulaa…ďe makko …ďen. ∆äuum ko …ďural Allah ngal o okkata on mo O muuyani. Allah ko Joim …ďural mawnungal."
  57,22,"Bone woo he…ďataa [on] e lesdi ndiin ma e pittaali mon …óiin, si wonaa …óuum woniino e deftere ado min tagude ndee [tagoore]. Pellet, …óuum ko ko newanii Allah."
  57,23,"Ko fii wota on cuno e ko laawii on kon, ngonaa kadi weltorgol ko o okki on kon. Allah yi…óaa kala √Īaa∆īoowo, mantii…óo."
  57,24,"∆Āeen wuddoo…ďe …ďe njamira yim…ďe …ďeen nguddam... kala …óuurnii…óo, pellet, Allah kan ko Galo, jettinii…óo."
  57,25,"GooŇč…óii Min nulirii Nulaa…ďe amen …ďeen …ďanngannduyeeji, Min njippindinani …ďe defte e sariyaare, fii no yim…ďe …ďeen √Īii…ďira e nun…óal. Min njippini kadi njamndi ndiin, ndi doole tii…óu…óe woni e mum e nafooje wonan'de yim…ďe …ďeen, e no Allah fe√Ī√Īinira …ďeen walloo…ďe mo e Nulaa…óo makko on ka wirnii. Pellet, Allah ko Jom demmbe, poolu…óo."
  57,26,"GooŇč…óii Min nulii Nuuhu e Ibraahiima, Min ma…ói e ge√Īngol ma…ď…ďe ngol Annabaaku e defte. Hino e ma…ď…ďe feewu…ďe, ko …óuu…ói kon e ma…ď…ďe ko faasiqii…ďe."
  57,27,"Refti Min njokkindini e batteeji ma…ď…ďe …óin, nulaa…ďe amen [goo], Min njokkintiniri […ďe] Iisaa ge…óal Maryama on, Min ngokki mo Linjiila, Min mba…ói e …ďer…óe jokku…ďe mo …ďen : yurmeende e giggol. Labbeyaagal ngal …ďe sinci ngal, Minen Min mba…ó…óinaa ngal e ma…ď…ďe. [Min lamndaaki] si wonaa …óa…ď…ďugol welayee Allah. Kono …ďe ayniraali …óum no haani aynireede. Min ngokki njo…ďdi goiŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen e ma…ď…ďe. Ko …óuu…óunoo kon e ma…ď…ďe ko faasiqii…ďe."
  57,28,"Eey mon yo gooŇč…óii…ďe! Kulee Allah, ngooŇč…óinon Nulaa…óo makko on; O ye…óay on ge…óe …ói…ói e mbarjaari makko ndiin, O wa…óana on annoora mo ndayginorton, O haforana on. Pellet, Allah ko kaforoowo, jurmootoo…óo."
  57,29,"Fii no yim…ďe defte …ďeen ngnndira won'de …ďe kattanaa hay hu'unde e …ďural Allah ngal, e won'de …ďural ngal ko e juu…óe Allah woni; Himo ye…óa ngal mo O muuyani. Pellet, Allah ko Joom …ďural manngal."
